Package: adas.utils
Title: Utility functions for the ADAS course, University of Trento, Italy
Version: 0.4.3
Authors@R: 
    person("Paolo", "Bosetti", , "paolo.bosetti@unitn.it", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Utility functions for the ADAS course, University of Trento, Italy. The package contains functions to deal with Design of Experiments (DoE) factoral plans, with the addition of some utility function to perform some statistical analyses.
